me.Abhigya.core.util.loadable

Interface Loadable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Validable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Configurable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConfigurableDuration, ConfigurableEnchantment, ConfigurableItemStack, ConfigurableLocation

    public interface Loadable
extends Validable
    Represents the classes that can be loaded from a ConfigurationSection.

    Note:

    Every single class that implements this interface must to have an empty constructor whose will act as 'uninitialized constructor', then the method loadEntries(ConfigurationSection) can create uninitialized instances and initialize it by using the method load(ConfigurationSection), that may initialize that instance correctly.
